OL,3,CMPs 'flabbergasted' as gambling boss
OL,4,Cdenies industry causes social harm
OL,6,FGrainne Hurst repeatedly said she
OL,7,Fdisagreed that gambling is a cause of
OL,8,Fsocial ills
OL,10,FMPs have raised concerns about
OL,11,Fevidence given to Parliament by the
OL,12,Fchief executive of the gambling
OL,13,Findustry's trade body.
OL,15,FGrainne Hurst, who leads the Betting
OL,16,Fand Gaming Council, appeared before
OL,17,Fthe Treasury Select Committee as the
OL,18,Fchancellor faces calls to increase
OL,19,Ftaxes on betting firms in next month's
OL,20,FBudget.
