OL,3,CMPs 'flabbergasted' as gambling boss
OL,4,Cdenies industry causes social harm
OL,6,FSome MPs appeared visibly frustrated
OL,7,Fby her evidence.
OL,9,FIn a statement, Chair of the Treasury
OL,10,FSelect Committee, Dame Meg Hillier MP,
OL,11,Fsaid: "While I accept parts of the
OL,12,Fgambling industry make an economic and
OL,13,Fcultural contribution to the UK, I am
OL,14,Ffrankly flabbergasted that
OL,15,Frepresentatives from the betting
OL,16,Fsector could not accept that certain
OL,17,Fforms of gambling, such as highly
OL,18,Faddictive online casino games, cause
OL,19,Fsocial harm for some people. I don't
OL,20,Fbelieve that is a defensible position."
