OL,4,Cdenies industry causes social harm
OL,6,FThe Institute for Public Policy
OL,7,FResearch (IPPR) estimates that the
OL,8,Fgovernment could raise an extra #3.2
OL,9,Fbillion a year by increasing taxes on
OL,10,Fonline gambling, physical slot
OL,11,Fmachines and sports betting.
OL,13,FFormer prime minister Gordon Brown has
OL,14,Fbacked the proposal, saying the money
OL,15,Fshould be used to lift the cap on
OL,16,Fbenefits for families with more than
OL,17,Ftwo children.
